Package: bodhi-lightdm-theme
Version: 1.13
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Jeff Hoogland <jeffhoogland@linux.com>
Depends: ttf-ubuntu-font-family, lightdm-gtk-greeter, bodhi-theme-moksha-arc-dark, faenza-icon-theme
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Description: Bodhi LightDM setup
 The lightdm greeter theme and configuration
 used for a standalone Bodhi installation.
 .
 This package can also be installed on
 other Ubuntu desktops desiring to use this
 theme, but it will replace the LightDM gtk theme.
